---
title: Tandoori Spiced Chicken Breast Tikka Masala with Spinach and Garlic Butter Rice
description: Tandoori gets its name from 'tandoor', an Indian cylindrical clay oven. Our tandoori spice mix includes cinnamon, turmeric, ginger and cumin, bringing the toasty flavours of a tandoor oven to this delicious masala curry.
